32
00:02:06,469 --> 00:02:09,450
<i>[Adapted from Beifeng Sanbaili's original novel "Memory of Encaustic Tile"]</i>

33
00:02:09,450 --> 00:02:12,020
<i>[Episode 21]
[A Step into the Adult World]</i>

34
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:17,959
Ms. Kang, is today an important occasion?

35
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:20,510
What's with all the delicious food?

36
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:34,180
Today...

37
00:02:40,900 --> 00:02:44,430
Today is his death anniversary.

38
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:50,900
Actually, I don't even know if it's today.

39
00:02:50,900 --> 00:02:56,630
His body was discovered three days after he jumped into the lake.

40
00:02:56,630 --> 00:03:00,330
That's why I don't want to face these three days

41
00:03:00,330 --> 00:03:03,360
in a sober manner every year.

42
00:03:09,770 --> 00:03:11,180
I guess I was being too much just now.

43
00:03:11,180 --> 00:03:14,389
Why did I tell you all of these things?

44
00:03:14,389 --> 00:03:17,940
You're still young. Now, you just need to believe

45
00:03:17,940 --> 00:03:20,820
that this world is filled with great things.

46
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:31,290
Ms. Kang, your makeup today looks amazing.

47
00:03:31,290 --> 00:03:32,999
Can you teach me how to put on makeup?

48
00:03:32,999 --> 00:03:34,629
My makeup skills were terrible back then.

49
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:37,590
Zhang Qi even teased me for it.

50
00:03:39,090 --> 00:03:41,909
Okay. I'll teach you how to put on makeup.

51
00:03:42,740 --> 00:03:46,420
If you two still don't agree to it, I'll skip school tomorrow as well.

52
00:03:46,420 --> 00:03:50,560
My dear daughter, when will you stop being willful?

53
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,580
The teacher said I had potential!

54
00:03:52,580 --> 00:03:54,690
Why can't you guys just agree to it?

55
00:03:54,690 --> 00:03:56,469
This time, your father and I will stop spoiling you.

56
00:03:56,469 --> 00:03:58,090
We will never agree to it.

57
00:03:58,090 --> 00:03:59,329
I won't eat if you two disagree!

58
00:03:59,329 --> 00:04:01,430
Suit yourself!

59
00:04:01,430 --> 00:04:03,309
I want to take up broadcasting! That's what I want to learn!

60
00:04:03,309 --> 00:04:05,700
I'll take the exam even if you two don't agree to it!

61
00:04:06,710 --> 00:04:09,759
How dare you do that! Come here!

62
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:12,799
Why are you here?

63
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:15,930
Shiyin, why have you been skipping school lately?

64
00:04:15,930 --> 00:04:18,020
That's none of your business!

65
00:04:18,020 --> 00:04:21,620
- Shiyin.
- Stop following me!

66
00:04:21,620 --> 00:04:24,720
Where... Where are you going?

67
00:04:38,650 --> 00:04:42,080
Shiyin, if you really don't know where to go,

68
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:44,360
let me bring you somewhere.

69
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:46,299
Is this the place you mentioned?

70
00:04:46,299 --> 00:04:48,940
Have a seat.

71
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:50,900
Wait for me.

72
00:04:59,820 --> 00:05:03,830
What are you doing? I don't eat junk food.

73
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:05,770
They aren't meant to be eaten.

74
00:05:05,770 --> 00:05:08,820
They're meant to be crushed.

75
00:05:17,390 --> 00:05:21,120
This is how I vent my anger whenever I'm angry.

76
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:23,530
So childish.

77
00:05:23,530 --> 00:05:25,480
Give it a try.

78
00:05:26,950 --> 00:05:29,140
It's really effective.

79
00:05:30,850 --> 00:05:36,689
Heaven and earth, god of instant noodles, show yourself.

80
00:05:41,190 --> 00:05:44,429
It's really effective. Just give it a try.

81
00:05:45,740 --> 00:05:50,970
<i>[Mala-flavored instant noodles]</i>

82
00:06:27,260 --> 00:06:30,800
What do you think? Do you feel better?

83
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,630
I guess.

84
00:06:34,060 --> 00:06:38,409
So what did you do when you skipped school for the past few days?

85
00:06:40,020 --> 00:06:42,380
I went to take a broadcasting class.

86
00:06:42,380 --> 00:06:46,010
But my mother isn't happy with it.

87
00:06:46,010 --> 00:06:49,620
So why did you take up broadcasting in the first place?

88
00:06:50,190 --> 00:06:53,040
I was born to be a host, okay?

89
00:06:53,650 --> 00:06:56,470
- How dare you laugh at me?
- I'm not laughing at you.

90
00:06:56,470 --> 00:06:59,979
I just think that this can't be considered a valid reason.

91
00:07:01,580 --> 00:07:03,800
Have you been a host before?

92
00:07:05,290 --> 00:07:09,040
I've only done it at the school's radio station.

93
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:13,819
I'm afraid you won't be able to convince your parents with this.

94
00:07:13,819 --> 00:07:17,789
You need to let them witness your performance as a host.

95
00:07:19,530 --> 00:07:21,820
So what should I do?

96
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:26,800
I have an idea. The place I worked in is going to hold their anniversary celebration soon.

97
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:29,899
I'll beg my supervisor to let you be the emcee of that event.

98
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:32,039
An emcee for an event?

99
00:07:32,039 --> 00:07:34,400
At least you can be on stage.

100
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:37,189
Moreover, how can you be on TV

101
00:07:37,190 --> 00:07:39,409
if you don't even dare to show yourself on small stages?

102
00:07:39,409 --> 00:07:40,719
Who said I don't dare to show up?

103
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,580
Fine, I'll go.

104
00:07:54,090 --> 00:07:56,389
Xue, you're so beautiful.

105
00:07:56,390 --> 00:07:58,270
Ms. Kang, it's all thanks to your amazing makeup skills.

106
00:07:58,270 --> 00:08:00,470
My mother couldn't do it.

107
00:08:00,470 --> 00:08:06,260
Xue, your future husband must be a very lucky man.

108
00:08:08,420 --> 00:08:10,860
<i>[Math Olympiad]</i>

109
00:08:12,850 --> 00:08:15,370
Both of them aren't back yet?

110
00:08:21,620 --> 00:08:23,039
I'm back.

111
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:24,199
Xue, you're back?

112
00:08:24,199 --> 00:08:25,770
Wait a minute!

113
00:08:25,770 --> 00:08:27,940
How's Ms. Kang?

114
00:08:30,210 --> 00:08:33,400
- She'll be fine after a few days.
- Good. Wait!

115
00:08:35,420 --> 00:08:37,140
Did you put on makeup?

116
00:08:37,140 --> 00:08:40,290
Ms. Kang did my makeup for me. Do I look good?

117
00:08:40,290 --> 00:08:42,270
- You look great.
- Keep this from Mom, okay?

118
00:08:42,270 --> 00:08:44,100
I know!

119
00:08:44,100 --> 00:08:45,400
Where's Mom?

120
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,589
She went to Ms. Ji Lan's house.

121
00:08:46,589 --> 00:08:49,249
- They said they were going to talk about Shiyin.
- Okay, then.

122
00:08:49,249 --> 00:08:50,700
Wait!

123
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:53,689
Come. Zhang Qi came to find you just now.

124
00:08:53,689 --> 00:08:55,820
These are the Math Olympiad books he gave you.

125
00:08:55,820 --> 00:08:57,320
Why did he give these to me?

126
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:59,299
He said as long as you can complete these questions,

127
00:08:59,299 --> 00:09:00,809
you'll be fine for the NCEE.

128
00:09:00,809 --> 00:09:02,180
He overestimated my abilities.

129
00:09:02,180 --> 00:09:03,360
I can't even understand basic math.

130
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:05,570
And he wants me to study for the Math Olympiad?

131
00:09:05,570 --> 00:09:07,840
Sunian came to find you as well.

132
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,899
He said he was going to take a one-month trip to find inspiration for his drawings.

133
00:09:09,899 --> 00:09:14,849
Before he departs, he wants you to accompany him to visit Ms. Jin Ning's grave together.

134
00:09:15,380 --> 00:09:17,289
I'll give him my reply right now.

135
00:09:17,289 --> 00:09:20,099
No need for that. I said yes on your behalf.

136
00:09:20,099 --> 00:09:23,160
I knew that you would surely go with him.

137
00:09:23,160 --> 00:09:25,060
Thank you, Dad.

138
00:09:25,060 --> 00:09:27,140
- Where are you going?
- I'm returning to my room.

139
00:09:27,140 --> 00:09:29,770
You better remove your makeup. Your mother will return soon.

140
00:09:29,770 --> 00:09:31,410
You're right!

141
00:09:34,620 --> 00:09:36,450
Wu Huan, what's going on?

142
00:09:36,450 --> 00:09:38,620
It's something good.

143
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:40,549
This child told us nothing.

144
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:43,040
- What kind of place is this? It's crowded.
- We're here.

145
00:09:43,040 --> 00:09:45,719
Mister, let's put aside the lucky draw for now.
<i>[Grand Opening Sale]</i>

146
00:09:45,719 --> 00:09:47,360
Tell me your wish first.

147
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:49,549
I wish to get a washing machine.

148
00:09:49,550 --> 00:09:50,980
- A washing machine?
- That's right.

149
00:09:50,980 --> 00:09:55,340
Do you have many family members and plenty of clothes to wash?

150
00:09:55,340 --> 00:09:56,800
That's right.

151
00:09:56,800 --> 00:10:00,870
I'm sure you have a thriving family and have plenty of children and grandchildren.

152
00:10:00,870 --> 00:10:02,280
That's right.

153
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:05,829
Since you're so fortunate, I'm sure you must be very lucky.

154
00:10:05,829 --> 00:10:08,340
Let us give this old mister our blessings.

155
00:10:08,340 --> 00:10:10,079
Let's hope he can achieve his wish. What do you guys think?

156
00:10:10,079 --> 00:10:12,170
<i>- Great!
- Sure!</i>

157
00:10:12,170 --> 00:10:14,490
Is that even Shiyin?

158
00:10:14,490 --> 00:10:17,210
- Okay, draw your lot.
- Yeah.

159
00:10:19,140 --> 00:10:23,200
This child doesn't behave like this usually.

160
00:10:24,340 --> 00:10:27,540
We spoiled her rotten at home.

161
00:10:27,540 --> 00:10:29,940
Actually, Shiyin is pretty amazing.

162
00:10:29,940 --> 00:10:32,820
She's performing very well considering it's her first time doing it.
- But...you will get another chance in the future.

163
00:10:32,820 --> 00:10:36,140
- Mister. Madam. I'm sure you two are most concerned about Shiyin.

164
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:38,549
This time, she isn't being willful. She's serious about it.

165
00:10:38,549 --> 00:10:40,809
- <i>Did I get the prize?</i>
- <i>Let's look at them one at a time.</i>

166
00:10:40,809 --> 00:10:43,340
One at a time!

167
00:10:44,030 --> 00:10:46,850
Did I get the prize?

168
00:11:03,570 --> 00:11:09,150
Sunian... this is your first time here, right?

169
00:11:10,380 --> 00:11:13,220
Actually, it's my first time here as well.

170
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:16,629
Actually, I was pretty afraid.

171
00:11:16,630 --> 00:11:20,530
I was afraid that I might have become dumber and uglier.

172
00:11:20,530 --> 00:11:23,339
What should I do if I didn't live up to Ms. Jin Ning's expectations?

173
00:11:23,339 --> 00:11:25,240
If I were as exceptional as you,

174
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:28,809
I'm sure I can visit Ms. Jin Ning with my head held high.

175
00:11:35,900 --> 00:11:37,630
Let's go.

176
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:47,650
Sunian, it's over here.

177
00:11:48,630 --> 00:11:52,909
<i>[Grave of Ms. Jin Ning]</i>
Ms. Jin Ning, Sunian and I are here to visit you.

178
00:12:06,550 --> 00:12:12,669
Ms. Jin Ning, these are your favorite cakes and flowers.

179
00:12:12,669 --> 00:12:16,630
Sunian bought all of these especially for you.

180
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:25,299
Ms. Jin Ning, I've finished all the books you gave me.

181
00:12:25,299 --> 00:12:27,319
Now, my English result is very stable.

182
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:29,509
I almost got a full score for every subject except for the essays.

183
00:12:29,510 --> 00:12:31,290
I'm amazing, right?

184
00:12:31,290 --> 00:12:33,869
Shiyin has taken up broadcasting.

185
00:12:33,870 --> 00:12:36,439
In the future, she'll be a famous host.

186
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:37,929
If you were still around,

187
00:12:37,929 --> 00:12:40,550
I'm sure you'd watch her show every day.

188
00:12:40,550 --> 00:12:44,229
By the way, Siyuan and Qiaomu have become a couple.

189
00:12:44,229 --> 00:12:46,640
Oh, I forgot the main point.

190
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:49,919
Sunian is studying art now. He's trying to get into the Academy of Fine Arts.

191
00:12:49,919 --> 00:12:54,069
He's determined to complete the drawings you couldn't complete.

192
00:12:54,069 --> 00:12:56,269
I think this is a tough task to complete.

193
00:12:56,270 --> 00:13:00,100
But I think Sunian can surely do it.

194
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:08,160
Ms. Jin Ning, I'm sure you think I'm talking too much.

195
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:12,030
Why don't I ask Sunian to speak with you?

196
00:13:14,150 --> 00:13:16,210
Don't leave!

197
00:13:16,210 --> 00:13:18,670
I don't know what to say.

198
00:13:27,550 --> 00:13:29,850
Ever since she was hospitalized,

199
00:13:31,530 --> 00:13:34,210
I was so afraid that I had to stay behind my father.

200
00:13:34,210 --> 00:13:37,470
I only dared to speak when she spoke to me.

201
00:13:37,470 --> 00:13:39,870
On the day she left,

202
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:45,239
I actually had plenty of things I wanted to tell her.

203
00:13:45,239 --> 00:13:49,249
I wanted to tell her that I loved her and I admired her.

204
00:13:49,249 --> 00:13:53,000
I feel very proud whenever I call her "Mom."

205
00:13:53,820 --> 00:13:56,610
But I told her nothing.

206
00:13:56,610 --> 00:13:58,690
I just looked at her.

207
00:14:02,390 --> 00:14:04,820
I didn't say a word.

208
00:14:04,820 --> 00:14:06,480
She asked my father a question.

209
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:08,839
She thought I was afraid of her

210
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:10,480
because of her hideous looks.

211
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:13,400
I wanted to tell her that it wasn't the case.

212
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:15,240
It wasn't the case at all.

213
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:17,380
I was just afraid.

214
00:14:18,140 --> 00:14:20,450
The way she looked at me...

215
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:27,690
was filled with regret and distress.

216
00:14:28,540 --> 00:14:30,900
From her eyes,

217
00:14:31,870 --> 00:14:36,630
I could tell that she was wondering how I could cope...

218
00:14:40,670 --> 00:14:42,900
after she passed away?

219
00:14:49,870 --> 00:14:52,450
Xue, I regret my decision!

220
00:14:52,450 --> 00:14:55,199
I regret that I didn't tell her how I felt

221
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,509
when she was still alive.

222
00:14:56,510 --> 00:14:59,210
I regret that I didn't hug her...

223
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:01,670
and tell her,

224
00:15:03,450 --> 00:15:04,900
"Mom,

225
00:15:05,650 --> 00:15:08,180
I do love you very much.

226
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:12,880
You're not scary at all.

227
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:19,749
You've always been the mother whom I admired the most."

228
00:15:25,510 --> 00:15:28,050
But I told her nothing.

229
00:15:29,020 --> 00:15:31,840
Now, she's gone.

230
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:34,400
It's useless for me to say all of these

231
00:15:34,400 --> 00:15:36,960
in front of her grave.

232
00:15:40,650 --> 00:15:42,760
She can't hear me anyway.

233
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:52,960
Sunian, that's not true.

234
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:55,550
As long as they're your heartfelt words,

235
00:15:55,550 --> 00:15:59,470
I'm sure Ms. Jin Ning can hear you.

236
00:16:08,030 --> 00:16:09,650
Mom,

237
00:16:12,220 --> 00:16:14,690
I won't disappoint you.

238
00:16:21,462 --> 00:16:26,402
Ms. Jin Ning, please give Sunian your blessings.

239
00:16:26,402 --> 00:16:29,962
Please wish for his success on the art exam, NCEE,

240
00:16:29,962 --> 00:16:32,622
and everything else.

241
00:17:03,632 --> 00:17:06,741
Shiyin, what did your parents say?

242
00:17:06,741 --> 00:17:08,612
They agreed to it.

243
00:17:08,612 --> 00:17:09,982
This is great.

244
00:17:09,982 --> 00:17:12,001
You're great at this. I'm sure everyone will like you

245
00:17:12,001 --> 00:17:14,442
when they see you on TV.

246
00:17:16,342 --> 00:17:18,171
All right then. If there's nothing else,

247
00:17:18,171 --> 00:17:21,322
I'll return home first. Goodbye.

248
00:17:22,372 --> 00:17:24,332
Wait.

249
00:17:24,332 --> 00:17:27,581
<i>[Liuli Hutong]</i>

250
00:17:27,582 --> 00:17:29,281
Is there anything else?

251
00:17:29,281 --> 00:17:31,962
Just tell me if you need anything.

252
00:17:41,062 --> 00:17:42,812
Thank you.

253
00:18:17,062 --> 00:18:19,302
Thank you, Wu Huan.

254
00:18:22,202 --> 00:18:23,762
See you.

255
00:19:12,500 --> 00:19:16,310
<i>[Xiaoyao Pavillion]
("Xiaoyao" means "carefree")</i>

256
00:19:35,142 --> 00:19:37,102
Your drawing is pretty good.

257
00:19:37,862 --> 00:19:40,102
You're the student of the master indeed.

258
00:19:42,442 --> 00:19:45,082
Maybe I'm not gifted at all.

259
00:19:46,412 --> 00:19:48,942
If I can't get into the Academy of Fine Arts by this year,

260
00:19:49,512 --> 00:19:51,752
I'll find myself a job.

261
00:19:51,752 --> 00:19:54,882
Why don't you try enrolling in another academy?

262
00:19:54,882 --> 00:19:57,232
You don't understand.

263
00:19:59,042 --> 00:20:01,711
When you truly like one thing,

264
00:20:01,712 --> 00:20:04,132
it's impossible for you to compromise.

265
00:20:05,032 --> 00:20:07,132
Just like women.

266
00:20:07,132 --> 00:20:09,732
Even if I can't marry you,

267
00:20:10,542 --> 00:20:12,952
I still love you.

268
00:20:12,952 --> 00:20:15,522
Even if I do marry another woman,

269
00:20:15,522 --> 00:20:17,682
I will be unsatisfied.

270
00:20:19,472 --> 00:20:22,132
You're still young. You'll understand when you grow up.

271
00:20:43,770 --> 00:20:48,970
♫ <i>Still the youngster from the past</i> ♫

272
00:20:48,970 --> 00:20:51,890
♫ <i>As pure as before</i> ♫

273
