283
00:21:26,371 --> 00:21:30,811
You must take note of the contrasts.

284
00:21:30,811 --> 00:21:33,691
From the top section to the bottom intersecting section of the light and dark part,

285
00:21:33,691 --> 00:21:36,331
that's where you should focus on the tone.

286
00:21:36,331 --> 00:21:38,001
Secondly, it's the shadow.

287
