303
00:22:29,520 --> 00:22:33,179
♫ <i>The future reunion</i> ♫

304
00:22:33,179 --> 00:22:35,281
♫ <i>Waving doesn't mean goodbye</i> ♫

305
00:22:35,281 --> 00:22:38,282
"It will be long before we can meet again after we part ways.

306
00:22:38,282 --> 00:22:40,516
"It will be long before we can meet again after we part ways.
<i>[Bells Ringing in the Rain, Liu Yong, Song Dynasty]</i>

307
00:22:40,517 --> 00:22:43,780
Fine moments and beautiful scenes will mean nothing to me.

308
00:22:44,332 --> 00:22:48,712
Though I have a thousand amorous feelings to confide,

309
00:22:48,712 --> 00:22:52,231
<i>[Sunian, you can do it]</i>
no sympathetic ear can I find."

