♫ <i>were brought back to the road by the wind</i> ♫

315
00:23:28,210 --> 00:23:36,400
♫ <i>Towards the future with courage</i> ♫

316
00:24:11,540 --> 00:24:17,419
<i>[Academy of Fine Arts Batch 2004 Admission List]</i>

317
00:24:17,420 --> 00:24:21,170
<i>[Traditional Chinese Painting, Zheng Sunian]</i>

318
00:24:22,822 --> 00:24:24,481
Did Sunian receive his admission notice?

319
00:24:24,481 --> 00:24:26,012
Yeah.

320
00:24:26,012 --> 00:24:28,742
Now, everyone else can let out a sigh of relief.

321
00:24:28,742 --> 00:24:31,482
This child is exceptional.

322
00:24:31,482 --> 00:24:33,281
It's hard to get into that academy.

323
00:24:33,281 --> 00:24:35,031
But he did it anyway.

324
00:24:35,031 --> 00:24:36,912
He suffered a lot for it.

325
00:24:36,912 --> 00:24:38,541
There were plenty of medicinal patches

326
00:24:38,542 --> 00:24:40,092
on his arms and shoulders.

327
00:24:40,092 --> 00:24:42,991
Zheng said it was the effect of practicing his drawing 24/7.

328
00:24:42,991 --> 00:24:46,992
I think he didn't suffer for nothing since he got into the academy.

329
00:24:50,572 --> 00:24:53,072
Only Xue is left.

330
00:24:53,072 --> 00:24:55,582
You're only nervous now?

331
00:25:26,332 --> 00:25:27,861
Sunian!

332
00:25:27,862 --> 00:25:29,632
Mr. Zheng!

333
00:25:29,632 --> 00:25:33,632
Sunian! Sunian!

334
00:25:33,632 --> 00:25:35,332
What's the matter?

335
00:25:38,442 --> 00:25:40,851
Sunian, our hairdryer is broken.

336
00:25:40,851 --> 00:25:43,522
Can I borrow your hairdryer?

337
00:25:44,382 --> 00:25:45,962
Come in.

338
00:25:48,212 --> 00:25:51,512
Sunian, where's Mr. Zheng?

339
00:25:51,512 --> 00:25:53,482
He went out to buy breakfast.

340
00:25:57,622 --> 00:26:00,382
Next time, don't go outside when your hair is wet.

341
00:26:00,382 --> 00:26:02,552
It's because my hairdryer is broken.

342
00:26:11,302 --> 00:26:12,362
Let me do it.

343
00:26:12,362 --> 00:26:13,511
Let me blow your hair dry.

344
00:26:13,512 --> 00:26:14,711
It's okay. I can do it myself.

345
00:26:14,712 --> 00:26:16,911
The electricity will leak as it hasn't been used for a while.

346
00:26:16,912 --> 00:26:19,001
It's the same no matter who does it.

347
00:26:19,001 --> 00:26:20,241
I can block the current with my hand.

348
00:26:20,241 --> 00:26:20,991
That won't do.

349
00:26:20,992 --> 00:26:22,101
Electrifying my head is a better option.

350
00:26:22,102 --> 00:26:24,242
You need to use your hands to draw.

351
00:26:24,242 --> 00:26:26,102
Turn around.

352
00:26:34,362 --> 00:26:37,892
And here. This part is wet.

353
00:26:47,372 --> 00:26:50,101
It's almost done. I think it's okay now. Sunian, I'll leave now.

354
00:26:50,892 --> 00:26:52,851
No. It's not dry yet.

355
00:26:52,851 --> 00:26:54,712
You'll catch a cold.

356
00:27:31,962 --> 00:27:35,652
Sunian, I have something to discuss with you.

357
00:27:35,652 --> 00:27:37,342
What's the matter?

358
00:27:43,202 --> 00:27:45,721
Can you trim your bangs just a little bit?

359
00:27:45,721 --> 00:27:49,071
- Why?
- They're too long. They're blocking your eyes.

360
00:27:49,071 --> 00:27:51,932
You shouldn't let them block your beautiful eyes.

361
00:27:52,722 --> 00:27:55,192
Sunian, time for breakfast.

362
00:27:55,192 --> 00:27:57,962
Mr. Zheng, you're back?

363
00:27:57,962 --> 00:27:59,652
Xue?

364
00:27:59,652 --> 00:28:01,141
Have you eaten breakfast yet?

365
00:28:01,142 --> 00:28:02,761
- Not yet.
- Great timing.

366
00:28:02,761 --> 00:28:04,231
You can share it with Sunian.

367
00:28:04,232 --> 00:28:06,301
If this is not enough, I think there are some biscuits over there.

368
00:28:06,301 --> 00:28:08,762
Mr. Zheng, aren't you going to join us?

369
00:28:08,762 --> 00:28:10,101
I'll eat breakfast on my way to work.

370
00:28:10,101 --> 00:28:12,091
I have to go. It's time to work.

371
00:28:12,091 --> 00:28:14,431
- Goodbye, Mr. Zheng.
- Goodbye.

372
00:28:15,752 --> 00:28:19,002
Xue, accompany me to buy some fruit later.

373
00:28:19,002 --> 00:28:20,422
Sure.

374
00:28:21,432 --> 00:28:23,061
I need to send some fruit to Mr. Luo.

375
00:28:23,062 --> 00:28:24,381
I managed to get into the Academy of Fine Arts

376
00:28:24,382 --> 00:28:26,582
thanks to his guidance.

377
00:28:27,172 --> 00:28:29,731
What do you wish to eat? I'll buy some for you, too.

378
00:28:30,682 --> 00:28:32,872
Bananas, apples, pears, strawberries, oranges!

379
00:28:32,872 --> 00:28:36,022
Let's finish our breakfast and buy them!

380
00:28:36,022 --> 00:28:37,482
Okay.

381
00:28:41,762 --> 00:28:45,432
Mr. Qian, seems like your shop is fancier right now.

382
00:28:45,432 --> 00:28:47,481
Didn't you only sell apples and pears in the past?

383
00:28:47,481 --> 00:28:49,331
Look at all the fruits you have right now.

384
00:28:49,331 --> 00:28:51,141
People strive to improve themselves, right?

385
00:28:51,142 --> 00:28:54,702
I've purchased some high-quality fruits, too.

386
00:28:54,702 --> 00:28:56,961
How much does a box of cherries cost?

387
00:28:56,961 --> 00:28:59,411
Usually, it's 80 yuan. But I'll sell it to you for 60.

388
00:28:59,411 --> 00:29:02,612
60? This is daylight robbery! These are just big cherries.

389
00:29:02,612 --> 00:29:04,101
Who are you trying to fool?

390
00:29:04,102 --> 00:29:06,101
Mr. Qian, get me two boxes of them.

391
00:29:06,102 --> 00:29:08,011
- All right.
- Wait!

392
00:29:08,732 --> 00:29:10,781
I would rather swallow the money directly.

393
00:29:10,782 --> 00:29:12,271
It's my treat.

394
00:29:12,272 --> 00:29:13,711
Why are you being stingy?

395
00:29:13,712 --> 00:29:15,541
Even so, it's still your money.

396
00:29:15,542 --> 00:29:16,821
You need to save your money.

397
00:29:16,822 --> 00:29:19,551
You'll have to spend a lot when you're studying in the future.

398
00:29:19,551 --> 00:29:22,912
Forget it. How about this?

399
00:29:22,912 --> 00:29:25,312
You guys can have one for free.

400
00:29:32,092 --> 00:29:33,511
What do you think?

401
00:29:33,512 --> 00:29:36,122
- Isn't it sweet?
- It's pretty sweet.

402
00:29:36,122 --> 00:29:38,232
It's sweet and delicious.

403
00:29:38,232 --> 00:29:39,581
Since it's delicious, you should buy some.

404
00:29:39,581 --> 00:29:40,632
No, thanks.

405
00:29:40,632 --> 00:29:43,771
Well, that was a waste. Why didn't you guys invite me?

406
00:29:43,782 --> 00:29:45,172
I'm going to visit Mr. Luo later.

407
00:29:45,172 --> 00:29:47,502
I'm buying some fruits for him.

408
00:29:47,502 --> 00:29:48,721
Seems like no one else will remember me

409
00:29:48,721 --> 00:29:50,322
after we get into college.

410
00:29:50,322 --> 00:29:52,002
Goodbye.

411
00:29:53,202 --> 00:29:55,131
What do you want? Pick anything.

412
00:29:55,131 --> 00:29:56,832
It's my treat.

413
00:29:57,652 --> 00:30:00,571
If so, I want 10 boxes of cherries.

414
00:30:00,571 --> 00:30:02,471
- All right.
- Wait a minute!

415
00:30:02,471 --> 00:30:04,631
10 boxes? Are you taking a bath with them?

416
00:30:04,631 --> 00:30:07,041
- It's Sunian's treat anyway.
- You!

417
00:30:07,062 --> 00:30:10,431
So are you guys buying it or not? Can you guys make a decision?

418
00:30:10,431 --> 00:30:12,172
No, we're not buying them.

419
00:30:12,782 --> 00:30:15,061
Mr. Qian, you opened a stall?

420
00:30:15,062 --> 00:30:16,721
Ms. Deng.

421
00:30:16,721 --> 00:30:17,821
You guys are here, too?

422
00:30:17,822 --> 00:30:20,472
Aren't you setting up your stall today?

423
00:30:20,472 --> 00:30:21,991
I have to return to my hometown.

424
00:30:21,992 --> 00:30:23,471
But why?

425
00:30:23,472 --> 00:30:25,522
My son is getting married. I'm returning to help him out.

426
00:30:25,522 --> 00:30:28,072
If so, when will you come back?

427
00:30:29,062 --> 00:30:31,692
I'm not coming back.

428
00:30:33,042 --> 00:30:34,832
You're not coming back?

429
00:30:36,102 --> 00:30:39,191
We had the roujiamo you made since we were little.
<i>(Street food; primarily stewed pork served between bread. Called a Chinese hamburger)</i>

430
00:30:39,192 --> 00:30:42,191
Where should we get them when

431
00:30:42,192 --> 00:30:43,942
you're not coming back?

432
00:30:43,942 --> 00:30:47,332
She's right, Ms. Deng.

433
00:30:47,332 --> 00:30:49,341
When I hear that from you,

434
00:30:49,342 --> 00:30:50,711
I guess I didn't spend the past decade

435
00:30:50,712 --> 00:30:52,862
selling roujiamo in vain.

436
00:30:53,682 --> 00:30:57,472
Ms. Deng, please take care of yourself.

437
00:30:57,472 --> 00:30:59,652
We will miss you.

438
00:31:02,132 --> 00:31:05,041
You guys should also be obedient and take good care of yourselves.

439
00:31:05,041 --> 00:31:07,411
I still need to catch my train.

440
00:31:07,411 --> 00:31:08,821
See you.

441
00:31:08,822 --> 00:31:11,262
- Goodbye, Ms. Deng.
- Goodbye.

442
00:31:11,262 --> 00:31:13,051
Ms. Deng, have a safe trip.

443
00:31:13,051 --> 00:31:14,951
Okay, goodbye. See you guys.

444
00:31:14,952 --> 00:31:16,712
Have a safe trip.

445
00:31:22,232 --> 00:31:24,112
Ms. Deng is leaving.

446
00:31:24,112 --> 00:31:27,362
There's no roujiamo for us now.

447
00:31:27,362 --> 00:31:30,702
Mr. Qian, when are you leaving?

448
00:31:30,702 --> 00:31:33,141
Thank you for nothing. Can't you say something good for once?

449
00:31:33,142 --> 00:31:35,821
Besides, if I leave and close the shop,

450
00:31:35,822 --> 00:31:38,142
who will act as his substitute father when he fails his exam?

451
00:31:38,142 --> 00:31:39,761
Where can you stay and cry when you're upset?

452
00:31:39,761 --> 00:31:41,621
How can you coax her when she doesn't have a chance to cry?

453
00:31:41,622 --> 00:31:44,242
I'm pretty important, you know?

454
00:31:44,242 --> 00:31:46,101
How about this? Today,

455
00:31:46,102 --> 00:31:48,281
I'll forget about my profit.

456
00:31:48,281 --> 00:31:51,922
You guys can have this box of kumquat on the house.

457
00:31:53,382 --> 00:31:55,761
I wish you guys academic success.

458
00:31:55,761 --> 00:32:00,511
Remember, no matter how far you guys go, you'll find me

459
00:32:00,511 --> 00:32:03,902
as long as you're back here. Take it.

460
00:32:03,902 --> 00:32:06,521
Mr. Qian, you're something else.

461
00:32:06,521 --> 00:32:08,781
Hey, don't you guys want to know more

462
00:32:08,782 --> 00:32:10,902
about the cherries?

463
00:32:13,380 --> 00:32:15,010
<i>[Corner Sundry Shop]</i>

464
00:32:43,514 --> 00:32:45,513
Is this all you're going to bring?

465
00:32:45,513 --> 00:32:47,373
Two luggage bags are barely enough for me to fit all of my stuff.

466
00:32:47,373 --> 00:32:49,653
I'll be studying in Beijing. You're going to a new place.

467
00:32:49,653 --> 00:32:52,044
Of course, you'll have to bring plenty of stuff.

468
00:32:52,044 --> 00:32:54,764
But you're bringing too much stuff.

469
00:32:54,764 --> 00:32:57,743
I've collected a lot of comic books and games before this.

470
00:32:57,743 --> 00:33:00,803
Now that I have the time, of course, I need to bring them with me.

471
00:33:00,803 --> 00:33:01,964
You're heading to USTC.

472
00:33:01,964 --> 00:33:03,923
I heard life there is just like life in our senior year.

473
00:33:03,923 --> 00:33:05,934
You don't have time for entertainment.

474
00:33:06,794 --> 00:33:08,804
I'm different from them.

475
00:33:08,804 --> 00:33:11,984
That's right. You're thick-skinned.

476
00:33:11,984 --> 00:33:13,974
Xue, hurry up!

477
00:33:13,974 --> 00:33:16,923
It's your first day as a senior-year student. You mustn't be late.

478
00:33:17,654 --> 00:33:19,834
Xue, hurry up!

479
00:33:20,644 --> 00:33:21,654
Aren't you going to eat?

480
00:33:21,654 --> 00:33:22,753
I'm heading to Sunian's place.

481
00:33:22,753 --> 00:33:24,403
He's attending college for the first time today. I'll see him off.

482
00:33:24,403 --> 00:33:26,674
I'll come back for breakfast later.

483
00:33:26,674 --> 00:33:28,543
Hurry up! Don't be late!

484
00:33:28,543 --> 00:33:30,544
Take this with you.

485
00:33:32,274 --> 00:33:34,713
Dad, it's almost fall season now.

486
00:33:34,713 --> 00:33:35,923
There aren't that many mosquitoes.

487
00:33:35,923 --> 00:33:37,794
There are.

488
00:33:39,124 --> 00:33:41,233
<i>- Hello, Mr. Zheng.
- Xue.</i>

489
00:33:41,233 --> 00:33:42,994
Sunian!

490
00:33:43,604 --> 00:33:45,844
Why are you here?

491
00:33:45,844 --> 00:33:48,163
I slept here last night.

492
00:33:48,163 --> 00:33:49,843
Since I was going to leave soon,

493
00:33:49,843 --> 00:33:52,333
I came here to talk about life with Sunian.

494
00:33:52,334 --> 00:33:53,443
So what did you get out of your chat?

495
00:33:53,443 --> 00:33:54,893
Nothing.

